xpiry_date }}</b></p>\n        </div>\n        {%- endif %}\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-xs-12 text-center bolder\">\n            <img src=\"https://barcode.tec-it.com/barcode.ashx?data=Customer%3A+{{doc.parent_customer}}%0AEmployee%3A+{{doc.employee_name}}%0AEmployee+ID%3A+{{doc.employee_id}}%0ADesignation%3A+{{doc.designation}}&code=QRCode&eclevel=L\" style=\"width:30%!important;margin-top: 5px!important;\">\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n",
